{
  "_id": "bBsAVKQpS4oiqdjr",
  "name": "Boar Aspect",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "systems/pf1/icons/skills/blue_29.jpg",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>Those with the aspect of the boar are famously stubborn.</em><br><br><strong>Minor Form:</strong> You gain @Compendium[pf1.feats.O0e0UCim27GPKFuW]{Diehard}&nbsp;as a bonus feat.</p>\n<p>At 8th level, you add your Hit Dice to your Constitution when determining the negative number of hit points at which you die.<br><br><strong>Major Form: </strong>Your shape changes to that of a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.aonprd.com/MonsterDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Dire%20Boar%20(Daeodon)\">dire boar</a>&nbsp;. While in this form, you gain low-light vision, the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.aonprd.com/UMR.aspx?ItemName=Scent\">scent</a>&nbsp;ability, a gore attack (1d8), and a base speed of 40 feet.</p>\n<p>At 8th level you gain&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.aonprd.com/FeatDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Improved%20Natural%20Attack\">Improved Natural Attack</a>&nbsp;with your gore attack, and you gain&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.aonprd.com/UMR.aspx?ItemName=Powerful%20Charge\">powerful charge</a>&nbsp;(+1d8 on your gore attack).</p>\n<p>At 15th level, you gain 1 additional hit point per Hit Die you have, and you gain&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.aonprd.com/FeatDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Awesome%20Blow\">Awesome Blow</a>&nbsp;(Bestiary 314) as a bonus feat.<br><br><strong>Alternate Natural Attacks:</strong> Gore (P), hoof (B)</p>",
